Bauchi state Governor Bala Mohammed in self isolation after having contact with Atiku Abubaka’s son who has been tested positive of coronavirus.   LEADERSHIP reports that the governor’s Chief of Staff Ladan Salihu has posted on his twitter handle. Ladan Salihu said the governor was on the same flight with Atiku’s son from Lagos to Abuja. “They shook hands and exchanged pleasantries. “The governor and the rest of us have taken tests”, Ladan said on his handle.